    "P6, who was emotionally entangled with their past relationship, customized a chatbot to be their expartner and shared regrets that they had never expressed before; they also created a virtual girlfriend to explore an answer about what truly matters in a romantic relationship.",
    "P5, while experiencing an existentialism crisis due to work stress, actively sought intellectual insights from different well-known philosophers such as Sartre and Heidegger.",
    "Recalling their customization experience, P22 noted that customization can add \"purposes and specifics to conversations, and with the help of LLMs, the customized personas are vivid and distinct, allowing them to experience various conversation scenarios: \"if I set it to be a father, it knows to speak to me in the tone of a father.",
    "If it's set as a husband, it adopts the tone of a husband.",
    "The choice of words, and even the emotional support I get from it, are different depending on the role.\""
